data.description: The Enclave at Boyette stands out as one of the premier communities in the coveted FishHawk area. No need to wait for new construction when you can purchase this beautiful home built in 2017 that is ready for immediate occupancy. As you enter the gated community, you immediately notice how private and peaceful the neighborhood feels. Located near excellent A-rated schools, ample shopping, restaurants, state parks and so much more! If you are looking for a place to call home with plenty of room to spread out, this is a must-see. The layout can easily accommodate a multigenerational living situation or a large family. As you enter the property, there is a guest bedroom on the first floor with a full bath, complemented by an impressive open kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances and granite finishes with an oversized island, seamlessly connecting to the expansive family room. The upper level unveils a spacious open loft, four additional bedrooms, each with walk-in closets. There is also a notably large shared bath with a double vanity. The primary bedroom is also on the second floor, consisting of massive dual closets and a private en suite that provides a luxurious escape with separate sinks, vanities, a generous shower stall and a soothing garden tub. With remarkably low HOA fees and no CDD fees, this home represents an exceptional opportunity in a quaint and well-maintained neighborhood. Capture the opportunity to claim ownership of this exceptional property. Your dream home is ready and waiting for you!
